ism|q=yes|s=yes|s-search=Category:Liberalism|b=yes|v=yes|d=yes|d-search=Q6216}}\n{{Portal bar|Current events|Liberalism}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Liberalism| ]]\n[[Category:Egalitarianism]]\n[[Category:History of political thought]]\n[[Category:Human rights concepts]]\n[[Category:Individualism]]\n[[Category:Political culture]]\n[[Category:Secularism]]\n[[Category:Social theories]]\n", "name_user": "Shoreranger", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eMajor themes", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liberalism"}
