er role in ''[[Marvel: Ultimate Alliance 2]]'', appearing as a boss if the player chooses to fight for the anti-Registration side.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/09/15/touring-the-marvel-ultimate-alliance-2-universe|title=Touring the Marvel: Ultimate Alliance 2 Universe |last=Schedeen|first=Jesse|website=[[IGN]]|date=September 14, 2009|accessdate=2012-06-11|url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160503142917/http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/09/15/touring-the-marvel-ultimate-alliance-2-universe?page=15|archivedate=May 3, 2016}}</ref>\n* Black Widow appears in the ''[[Iron Man 2 (video game)|Iron Man 2]]'' video game, voiced by Catherine Campion.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://yourindustryinsider.com/2011/10/actress-voiceover-artist-catherine-campion|title=Industry Pro: Actress/Voiceover Artist Catherine Campion|last=Yerrick Martin|first=Jenny|publisher=Your Industry Insider|date=October 5, 2011|accessdate=June 28, 2012|url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120704163530/http://yourindustryinsider.com/2011/10/actress-voiceover-artist-catherine-campion/ |archivedate=July 4, 2012 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n* Black Widow appears as a playable character in the ''[[Marvel Super Hero Squad: The Infinity Gauntlet]]'' video game, voiced by [[Grey DeLisle]].<ref name=\"bwva\" />\n* Black Widow is a playable character in ''[[Marvel Super Hero Squad Online]]'', voiced by Laura Bailey.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vg247.com/2012/02/08/marvel-super-hero-squad-online-to-be-fully-voiced/|title=Marvel Super Hero Squad Online to be fully voiced|last=Hillier|first=Brenna|website=[[VG247]]|date=February 8, 2012|accessdate=April 21, 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906165318/http://www.vg247.com/2012/02/08/marvel-super-hero-squad-online-to-be-fully-voiced/|archivedate=September 6, 2015}}</ref>\n* Black Widow is a playable character in the [[Facebook]] game ''[[Marvel: Avengers Alliance]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://gamerant.com/avengers-alliance-facebook-characters/|title=Marvel's Avengers Alliance Adds X-Men & Fantastic Four Characters|last=Keyes|first=Rob|publisher=Gamerant|accessdate=April 1, 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401003414/https://gamerant.com/avengers-alliance-facebook-characters/|archivedate=April 1, 2019}}</ref>\n* Black Widow appears as a Heroes vs Heralds card in ''[[Ultimate Marvel vs Capcom 3]]''. If Hawkeye defeats ''[[Street Fighter|Street Fighter's]]'' [[Crimson Viper]], he'll say, \"Black Widow you ain't.\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.eventhubs.com/news/2011/oct/19/cards-listing-heroes-heralds-mode-umvc3/|title=Early card listing for Heroes & Heralds mode in Ultimate Marvel vs. Capcom 3|last=Grey|first=Jonathan|publisher=Eventhubs|date=October 19, 2011|accessdate=April 22, 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150116065704/http://www.eventhubs.com/news/2011/oct/19/cards-listing-heroes-heralds-mode-umvc3/|archivedate=January 16, 2015}}</ref>\n* Black Widow is a playable character in ''[[Marvel Contest of Champions]]'', and was granted to every player for participation in the Ultron tie-in quests.<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://variety.com/2015/digital/news/avengers-age-of-ultron-marvel-contest-of-champions-1201478216/|title=\u2018Avengers: Age of Ultron\u2019 Evil Robot Infests Mobile Game \u2018Marvel Contest of Champions\u2019|last=Spangler|first=Todd|magazine=Variety|date=April 23, 2015|accessdate=April 1, 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401042737/https://variety.com/2015/digital/news/avengers-age-of-ultron-marvel-contest-of-champions-1201478216/|archivedate=April 1, 2019}}</ref>\n* Black Widow appears as a playable character in the 2012 [[fighting game]] ''[[Marvel Avengers: Battle for Earth]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.polygon.com/2012/10/19/3524806/marvel-avengers-battle-for-earth-line-up-include-black-widow-doctor|title=Marvel Avengers Battle for Earth line-up includes Black Widow, Doctor Doom, Iro